  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="15691238">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gershom/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2861568-3.jpg" alt="雪莱" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15691238/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15691238/" class="">第5页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/gershom/" class=" " title="雪莱">雪莱</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="15691238">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">所有的人都是哲学家，每个人都无意识的各有一套哲学，因为哪怕是任何一种智力活动的最起码的表现，哪怕是在“语言”中，都包含着一套哲学观。</span>
                <p class="pl">
